 at servers with hardware RAID controllers.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
So the advice is clear: 
\series bold
switch them off
\series default
 
\emph on
in such a case
\emph default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Even if you have a software RAID, check with 
\family typewriter
blkreplay
\family default
