\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Although this big effort resulted in a somewhat working system, the result
 is was not fully HA.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Notice that HA is defined by a single number like 99.99% (see mars-architecture-g
uide.pdf).
 In practice, true HA 
\emph on
typically
\emph default
